					<description><![CDATA[I&#8217;m packing up my boy and heading up to San Francisco for the 2013, Alternative Press Expo!  I&#8217;ll be sharing a table with Janice T and Elizabeth Watasin, signing books and selling swag.  We&#8217;ll also be offering a Steampunk Bundle of all 4 books on offer, for a reduced price! So, if you&#8217;re in the SF bay [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.comic-con.org/ape" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="alignright" alt="" src="http://www.beatzo.net/blog/wp-content/uploads/APE-Logo.jpg" width="178" height="246" /></a>I&#8217;m packing up my boy and heading up to San Francisco for the 2013, <a href="http://www.comic-con.org/ape" target="_blank">Alternative Press Expo</a>!  I&#8217;ll be sharing a table with <a href="http://www.facebook.com/JaniceTPoems" target="_blank">Janice T</a> and <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ElizabethWatasinX" target="_blank">Elizabeth Watasin</a>, signing books and selling swag.  We&#8217;ll also be offering a Steampunk Bundle of all 4 books on offer, for a reduced price!</p>
<p>So, if you&#8217;re in the SF bay area on Oct 12th or 13th, come and see us!  APE looks like it&#8217;ll have a long list of fabulous artist, writers, and makers all under one roof, along with an impressive list of <a href="http://www.comic-con.org/ape/2013/special-guests" target="_blank">special guests</a>.  Check out <a href="http://www.comic-con.org/ape" target="_blank">their site</a> for more info.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m also going to try vloging again, so check on the 14th to see if I managed to do it!  Meanwhile, I designed some buttons to sell at the expo.  What do you think?  I really like the one with the top hat.<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignleft  wp-image-823" alt="three test 02" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/three-test-02.jpg" width="630" height="210" srcset="https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/three-test-02.jpg 900w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/three-test-02-300x100.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px" /></p>
<p>The expo will be held at <a href="http://www.sfvenues.com/concourse/overview.html" target="_blank">Concourse Exhibition Center</a> in San Francisco, CA, October 12th and 13th.  I hope to see you there!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
